*Vidjeti* ga je bilo pravo čudo. (To see him was a real miracle.)
Mislio sam da ću nikada *vidjeti* njegov osmijeh. (I thought I would never see his smile.)
*Vidjela* sam ga kako se šeta gradom. (I saw him walking around the town.)
Nisam očekivao da ću ikada *vidjeti* tu sliku. (I didn't expect to ever see that picture.)
Jedva sam *vidjela* njegovo lice. (I barely saw his face.)